cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CV 

Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper deals with sequence generation and language modeling tasks. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper proposes a new algorithm for sampling sequences using Stochastic Beam Search. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with generating diverse yet good quality translations. 
- cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is a possible category as the paper uses neural networks for language modeling. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is a less likely category as the paper does not deal with image or video data, but it is still possible as the proposed algorithm could potentially be applied to sequence generation tasks in computer vision.
